<number box="[764,806,655,679]" pageId="18" pageNumber="53" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5–6</number>
smaller basal teeth; dorsal surface of mandible striate; ventral margin of petiole with large translucent longitudinal flange, ventral margin of flange erose, with irregular jagged posteriorly-directed teeth; ventral margin of postpetiole with large, acute anteroventral tooth.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
